TAXES ON VESTING OF RESTRICTED STOCK. APPROXIMATELY 5,000 SHARES WERE REACQUIRED IN TRANSACTIONS OUTSIDE THE PROGRAM DURING THE QUARTER ENDED DECEMBER 31, 2010.

